g.text: It is, though. Because this is what I've been avoiding saying:

g.title: j2112574466
g.text: I.

g.title: j304823287
g.text: Am.

g.title: j4254602077
g.text: Duviri.

g.title: j1666063242
g.text: Check boolean ArthurFearSpiral

g.title: j812612635
g.text: All of the fear? All of that twisted terror that screams and cries at every shadow?

g.title: j1666063242->j812612635
g.text: true

g.title: j2992951070
g.text: Check boolean ArthurJoySpiral

g.title: j1666063242->j2992951070
g.text: false

g.title: j3417047614
g.text: That lashes out at everything and everyone around it?

g.title: j3547001852
g.text: All of the sickening false "joy" and beauty smeared on top of it like a bad birthday cake?

g.title: j2992951070->j3547001852
g.text: true

g.title: j3235680043
g.text: Check boolean ArthurEnvySpiral

g.title: j2992951070->j3235680043
g.text: false

g.title: j560276936
g.text: It comes from MY head. It isn't just a product of the book, Arthur. It's from ME.

g.title: j965957798
g.text: Covering the warts and the rot underneath? Trying to hide what it really is?!

g.title: j2407528038
g.text: All of that horrid envy and jealousy that poisons everything around it?

g.title: j3235680043->j2407528038
g.text: true

g.title: j3433941800
g.text: Check boolean ArthurAngerSpiral

g.title: j3235680043->j3433941800
g.text: false

g.title: j2327137955
g.text: I did it to myself... all of it. Over, and over... and over... and over...

g.title: j1783635924
g.text: That wants to have what everybody else had? A normal life? A family? Friends?

g.title: j4283771949
g.text: All of that rage, that hatred, that burning anger?

g.title: j3433941800->j4283771949
g.text: true

g.title: j1040532951
g.text: Check boolean ArthurSorrowSpiral

g.title: j3433941800->j1040532951
g.text: false

g.title: j2181674763
g.text: Until it just... took it all away. Until I couldn't feel any of it anymore.

g.title: j3701676513
g.text: That wanted nothing more than to rip the sinew from the bones of the people who had hurt me?

g.title: j3306462059
g.text: The crushing sorrow that made me want to do nothing but sink to the bottom of an abyss?

g.title: j1040532951->j3306462059
g.text: true

g.title: j3191405531
g.text: All of that suffering, all of that endless pain, and death?!

g.title: j1040532951->j3191405531
g.text: false

g.title: j755006271
g.text: Until feeling nothing was better than feeling anything at all.

g.title: j4223938853
g.text: To fall on my own sword, if it wouldn't have been pointless?

g.title: j2113541552
g.text: All those insipid courtiers and all the endless executions they put me through?

g.title: j1405909456
g.text: It was so bad, Arthur, I began to forget. Forget who I was. What I was.

g.title: j399086099
g.text: Where I came from.

g.title: j563135247
g.text: Check boolean ArthurDuviriExternal

g.title: j3612878880
g.text: Maybe I thought, deep down inside, if I forgot about the people I blamed for putting me in Duviri?

g.title: j563135247->j3612878880
g.text: true

g.title: j1845441255
g.text: Check boolean ArthurDuviriInternal

g.title: j563135247->j1845441255
g.text: false

g.title: j2412384711
g.text: Maybe then, it'd end... one way or another.

g.title: j3854105561
g.text: Maybe I thought, deep down inside, if I forgot that Duviri was really all my fault?

g.title: j1845441255->j3854105561
g.text: true

g.title: j535344559
g.text: Maybe I thought, deep down inside, that if I forgot everything?

g.title: j1845441255->j535344559
g.text: false

g.title: j3917722164
g.text: If it weren't for Lotus and Teshin...

g.title: j2687204062
g.text: I'd still be there. A shell. A ghost. Empty. Forgotten and forgetting.

g.title: j1603886550
g.text: Check boolean ArthurApathy

g.title: j1477486575
g.text: So, yeah. You can argue with me about it all you want.

g.title: j1603886550->j1477486575
g.text: true

g.title: j2179050738
g.text: So when I say "Apathy is worse than anything else." That's what I mean.

g.title: j1603886550->j2179050738
g.text: false

g.title: j2286364444
g.text: But that's why apathy is worse.

g.title: j37965875
g.text: And why I'll never give up fighting it.

g.title: j2134778915
g.text: And you know what's really weird? I go back. I go back all the time.

g.title: j3826822418
g.text: Because I feel like I have a duty to those people there. They... they exist because of me.

g.title: j389541261
g.text: As busted as it is, as messed up as it sounds, it's the only real home I've ever known.

g.title: j2273591323
g.text: Nothing works out your anger quite like smashing up a place that you know resets constantly.

g.title: j107088951
g.text: Now that I know I can leave it... feels almost... fun again. I can find the joy in it again. As twisted as that is.

g.title: j1706560301
g.text: There. That's the story.

g.title: j2500287120
g.text: Ta-Da. The End.

g.title: j975958492
g.text: You there?

g.title: j1121063144
g.text: Check boolean ArthurDating

g.title: j2746336897
g.text: I'm here, love.

g.title: j1121063144->j2746336897
g.text: true

g.title: j2362582682
g.text: I'm here.

g.title: j1121063144->j2362582682
g.text: false

g.title: j3435773868
g.text: Sol above... I'm here.

g.title: j1838203067
g.text: Ugh, I think I'm going to cry.

g.title: j1795522062
g.text: Is that what you wanted to hear? You happy now?

g.title: j577403149
g.text: I'd be lying if I said you were the only one.

g.title: j1738161017
g.text: No. I'm not happy.

g.title: j1642755963
g.text: I... I had no idea you blamed yourself for what you went through.

g.title: j4267258726
g.text: Check boolean ArthurDating

g.title: j3586455389
g.text: How could I not? I literally made the place out of my own emotions.

g.title: j1523664265
g.text: Yeah, well. We all have our shit to deal with.

g.title: j1936667983
g.text: I'm heartbroken, love.

g.title: j4267258726->j1936667983
g.text: true

g.title: j928892436
g.text: I'm heartbroken.

g.title: j4267258726->j928892436
g.text: false

g.title: j1898194136
g.text: You were a CHILD. Who was forced to hunt down their own parents.

g.title: j3145819890
g.text: No. Don't do that. Don't dismiss this.

g.title: j704474158
g.text: Who was then left behind, all alone, to face *the Void.*

g.title: j1906190615
g.text: I'd wager good money that most grown adults - myself included - would crumple like a house of cards...

g.title: j4265216459
g.text: If we had to go through what you went through.

g.title: j2492975881
g.text: You did the absolute best you could. You survived.

g.title: j1238631207
g.text: And look what's become of you.

g.title: j3051484412
g.text: Savior of the Origin System - or whatever it's called.

g.title: j1780017826
g.text: Check boolean ArthurDating

g.title: j3120684229
g.text: And the one I adore most in this world.

g.title: j1780017826->j3120684229
g.text: true

g.title: j628688196
g.text: And one of my dearest friends.

g.title: j1780017826->j628688196
g.text: false

g.title: j489716073
g.text: So, you don't... think less of me, now?

g.title: j2076800265
g.text: You're going to make me cry again.

g.title: j1198630148
g.text: The opposite.

g.title: j1821448243
g.text: Yeah, well.

g.title: j4124357456
g.text: The absolute opposite.

g.title: j1309096053
g.text: Sometimes it's good for you.

g.title: j1372894846
g.text: I swear it.

g.title: j3913058672
g.text: Or so Lettie tells me.

g.title: j25209126
g.text: Check boolean ArthurDating

g.title: j1529924978
g.text: Thanks. That means... more than you can imagine.

g.title: j25209126->j1529924978
g.text: true

g.title: j3403956650
g.text: Thanks, Arthur. That means... more to me than you can imagine.

g.title: j25209126->j3403956650
g.text: false

g.title: j476514136
g.text: Now I need a damn drink.

g.title: j1593099216
g.text: +20 Chemistry

g.title: j1704159473
g.text: And I'm buying.
